kept the defense and reflected stormed the Nazis. Part of the forces of the enemy infantry tried to go through the Bush from the West, but was ostanovleno calculating machine gun, Bazooka knocked another Puma, which began poured out like mushrooms, and fled in different directions. Then again poper infantry, which took only 15 minutes for a retreat. Not yet cooled body lay on the snow, as if the Christmas gifts under the tree. Snow was again falling.We start to iron artilerry.Close Combat is one of the best series of tactical strategies that go back to 1994."
